You can call me Ellis but a few people used to know me by Sink. Stop calling me that. :)
I'm Genderfluid. You can call me by any pronouns.
DNI if you just want to bother me.

I can draw, I know that for sure.
In Roblox Studio specifically, I can animate and model. I use Blender for outlines.
I can also design concepts, but I doubt my abilities.

When it comes to things I like, I will always be excited for any Mario content.
I like Sonic the Hedgehog. I don't like his games because they're very jank. I like Sonic so much that I have my own OC based off of him. I love my OC and I won't share his details with you. :)

I can understand some French and Italian but I'm no expert at either of them.
If I unfriend you, it's because I don't talk to you or because I don't want a lot of friends. There are some exceptions, though, because even if I don't talk to some of my friends, I still think about talking to them. I'm a bit shy, so that's why I don't talk.

user_info.description:
Skibidi Toilet is a machinima web series of YouTube videos and shorts created by Alexey Gerasimov and uploaded on his YouTube channel produced using Source Filmmaker, the series follows a fictional war between human-headed toilets and humanoid characters with electronic devices for heads.

Since the first short was posted in February 2023, Skibidi Toilet has become viral as an internet meme across various social media platforms, particularly popularized by Generation Alpha. Many commentators saw the series as Generation Alpha's first foray into internet culture.
